{"tid":1850332,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：我唔帶口罩","createTime":"2020-01-29T13:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T11:14:21.000Z","uid":78768,"like":23,"dislike":374,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9f93eb7f69df855eb39fbeedf39502ffc6069e","tid":1850332,"uid":78768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8aQZv7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8aQZv7.png&h=1efce279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：今日在地鐵站，只有我和兩個外籍白人女子無戴口罩。<br />\n足以說明一切。<br />\n（按：大家不要學啊。戴口罩也可避免一般流感的。一般流感的繼發傳染率和死亡率遠遠高於沙士及現在的武漢肺炎，故此各位要時時刻刻戴口罩啊！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！游水都要戴。接吻更加要戴。洗熱水澡的霧氣傳播病毒更厲害，更加要戴加倍防護的口罩。）<br />\n閱讀智力門檻：IQ120."},{"pid":"a992b15e2cbbe4237222c18867af0ed74943818f","tid":1850332,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:05:41.000Z","msg":"[行動]連儂/文宣十八區開花! A4 label周圍貼! 大量現成圖-即print 即貼(3)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850261</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ea3e859c39c2268e514f792a564bc70389cfdee","tid":1850332,"uid":54511,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d3171f2bdcd21cee55006dd23645686d146e86","tid":1850332,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:06:28.000Z","msg":"6-14日開始計算。。"},{"pid":"c448d65a976c4139acaf804aa229d65e1b7f0539","tid":1850332,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3f59f5626c6ccaed91780d18e524a3a7230f96","tid":1850332,"uid":323700,"like":214,"dislike":2,"score":212,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:06:52.000Z","msg":"岩啦<br />\n我就係等緊呢條痴線佬死<br />\n記得中左招咪撚出街害人"},{"pid":"2d562c9e31dde54d1b0d5e81d25489680443f7ae","tid":18